Global Industrial Wastewater Treatment Service Market Insights
Industrial Wastewater Treatment Service Market size was valued at USD 62.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 85.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.4% from 2024 to 2030.

Industrial Wastewater Treatment Service Market Overview
The industrial wastewater treatment service market is witnessing significant growth driven by rising environmental regulations, increased industrial activities, and a greater focus on sustainability. As industries are producing more waste, wastewater treatment has become a critical component for ensuring environmental protection. In 2024, the market was valued at USD 15.8 billion and is projected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.2% from 2025 to 2030. The services include a variety of processes such as filtration, biological treatment, chemical treatment, and others, aimed at reducing contaminants and recycling water for further use. The rapid industrialization, along with stricter wastewater discharge norms, is propelling the demand for wastewater treatment services across various industries, including manufacturing, chemicals, and food processing.

